details: The primary materials that compose this product contain a minimum of 20 percent recycled content.

The sporty adidas® Dame 7 Extended Play Basketball Shoes are about giving credit where credit is due, featuring a Lightstrike midsole along with nods to the music industry throughout the upper. Breathable mesh and signature cushioning will leave your defenders in the dust.
This product is made with recycled content as part of adidas® ambition to end plastic waste. 20% of pieces used to make the upper are made with minimum 50% recycled content.
Reinforced knit uppers with breathable mesh panels.
Traditional lace-up closure for adjustable fit.
Lightstrike midsole with energy-returning technology for light, fast rebounding.

title: adidas Samba® Classic
details: Slightly more athletic than it's Originals brother—with an extended tongue geared for indoor play—the Samba® Classic from adidas® continues to provide that retro vibe in a solid, soccer-ready sneaker!
Full grain leather uppers with suede T-toe overlay.
Comfortable fabric lining and lightly cushioned footbed.
Traditional lace-up closure with an extended tongue for enhanced ball control and touch.
Gum rubber midsole with serrated foxing detail.
Gum rubber outsole for excellent traction.
